+## File Explorer Gate - 2026-06-09
+
+The next requested product surface is the file explorer for v5.
+
+Status: `PARTIAL`
+
+Decision:
+
+- UI implementation is still blocked until the feature has an explicit product/Figma gate record.
+- v0.dev or shadcn/ui output may be used only as an implementation source after the gate names the exact source prompt, generated files, review evidence, and rollback path.
+- No file-system read/write behavior is approved by this gate. The first pass must be a UI shell or mocked local data surface unless a separate filesystem permission decision exists.
+- No source repo product code may be copied into v5 without a migration-court sourceRef and file-level decision.
+
+Required evidence before implementation:
+
+- Feature scope: navigation tree, file list, breadcrumbs, search, empty state, selection, and settings entry points.
+- Design source: Figma frame link or v0.dev prompt/output reference.
+- Data boundary: static/mock, local read-only, or local read-write, with permission notes.
+- Validation plan: UI render evidence, responsive evidence, and no fake dashboard success.
+- Rollback note: normal git revert of the feature files must remove the feature without touching runtime state.
